  2 × 32;
  4 × 16;
  2 × 2 × 16;
  8 × 8;
  2 × 4 × 8;
  2 × 2 × 2 × 8;
  4 × 4 × 4;
  4 × 4 × 2 × 2;
  4 × 2 × 2 × 2 × 2;
  2 × 2 × 2 × 2 × 2 × 2.

CHECK
